<p>These messages offer a final note of hope and peace.</p>
<p>May the memories you cherish bring you comfort during this difficult time.  May peace find you, and may time heal your wounds.  Know that your loved one's spirit lives on in the hearts of those who loved them.  Remember the good times, and hold onto those memories tightly.  In time, the pain will lessen, and the memories will bring a smile. Grief is a journey, and though it may seem long and difficult now, healing and peace are possible.  Find strength in your love and support system.  You are not alone.</p>
    
  
